titles.title: Nothing, O Nothing, I Am Nothing At All

verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
Nothing, O Nothing, I am nothing at all.
(Repeat 4x.)
Mold me and make me because I am nothing at all.
(Repeat 4x.)
Try me and test me for I am nothing at all.
(Repeat 4x.)
Save me and help me; I am nothing at all.
(Repeat 4x.)
